Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.36,0:01:40.62,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur2}焰之月 好似燃燒殆盡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.95,0:01:47.43,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur2}沉沒在拂曉之中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.90,0:01:53.86,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur2}帶著偽造的臉龐 悄悄地靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.07,0:01:59.18,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur2}把信任的人 棄於黑暗之中
